Postgres::Handler
=================

NAME
        Postgres::Handler (perl extension)

DESCRIPTION
        Accessors for PostgreSQL data.  Simplifies data access through a series
        of standard class methods.

REQUIRES
        CGI::Carp
        CGI::Util
        Class::Struct
        DBI

INSTALLATION
        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

EXPORT
        None by default.

